{"data":[{"name":"83:1","price":"量を減らす者たちに災いあれ。¹","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُطَفِّفِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5849,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　このアーヤ*は、商取引において公正ではなかったマディーナ*の民に関して下ったとされる。そしてこのアーヤ*が下った後、彼らの商取引は改善された（イブン・マージャ２２２３参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun lil'muṭaffifīna ","translations":["Woe","to those who give less","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","lil'muṭaffifīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,4755]]}},{"name":"83:2","price":"（彼らは、）自分たちが（買うため、）人々に升（や秤¹）で量らせる時には、（自分たちの権利を）全うさせる者たち。","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ إِذَا ٱكۡتَالُواْ عَلَى ٱلنَّاسِ يَسۡتَوۡفُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5850,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「升」と「秤」の詳細については、家畜章１５３の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna idhā ik'tālū ʿalā al-nāsi yastawfūna ","translations":["Those who","when","they take a measure","from","the people","they take in full","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","idhā","ik'tālū","ʿalā","al-nāsi","yastawfūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,1620],[3,1620,2620],[4,2620,3010],[5,3010,4740],[6,4740,7945]]}},{"name":"83:3","price":"そして自分たちが（売るため、）彼らに升で量ったり、秤で量ったりする時には、（相手に）損させる（者たち）。","arabic":"وَإِذَا كَالُوهُمۡ أَو وَّزَنُوهُمۡ يُخۡسِرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5851,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā kālūhum aw wazanūhum yukh'sirūna ","translations":["But when","they give by measure (to) them","or","they weigh (for) them","they give less","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","kālūhum","aw","wazanūhum","yukh'sirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,2210],[3,2210,2500],[4,2500,3750],[5,3750,6895]]}},{"name":"83:4","price":"一体、彼らは自分たちが蘇らされ（て、応報を受け）る身であると、考えないのか？","arabic":"أَلَا يَظُنُّ أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ أَنَّهُم مَّبۡعُوثُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5852,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alā yaẓunnu ulāika annahum mabʿūthūna ","translations":["Do not","think","those","that they","(will be) resurrected","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["alā","yaẓunnu","ulāika","annahum","mabʿūthūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,2400],[3,2400,4610],[4,4610,6470],[5,6470,10305]]}},{"name":"83:5","price":"偉大なる（報いの）日*に？","arabic":"لِيَوۡمٍ عَظِيمٖ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5853,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"liyawmin ʿaẓīmin ","translations":["For a Day","Great","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["liyawmin","ʿaẓīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,4045]]}},{"name":"83:6","price":"人々が（行いの清算のため）、全創造物の主*（の御前）に立つ日。","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَقُومُ ٱلنَّاسُ لِرَبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5854,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yaqūmu al-nāsu lirabbi al-ʿālamīna ","translations":["(The) Day","will stand","mankind","before (the) Lord","(of) the worlds","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yaqūmu","al-nāsu","lirabbi","al-ʿālamīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1490],[3,1490,3130],[4,3130,3940],[5,3940,7905]]}},{"name":"83:7","price":"断じて（、彼らの状態は正しく）ない！本当に放逸なものたちの（行いが記録された）帳簿は、まさにスィッジーン¹の中にある。","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ كِتَٰبَ ٱلۡفُجَّارِ لَفِي سِجِّينٖ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5855,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「帳簿」の解釈には、文字通りの意味のほかにも、「行い」「魂と行い」といった説もある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：２５７参照）。「スィッジーン」は一説に、「スィジン（牢獄）」という語から派生した言葉で、地獄での幽閉（ゆうへい）と苦しみの原因であり、それ自体が牢獄のような屈辱（くつじょく）と懲罰の場所にあることが、その名称の由来とされる（イブン・ジュザイ２：５４８参照）。不信仰者*や不正*者の魂、彼らの行いの帳簿が置かれることになる、世界で最も低い場所のこと（アル＝ジャザーイリー５：５３５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā inna kitāba al-fujāri lafī sijjīnin ","translations":["Nay","Indeed","(the) record","(of) the wicked","(is) surely in","Sijjin","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","inna","kitāba","al-fujāri","lafī","sijjīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2559],[2,2559,3699],[3,3699,4509],[4,4509,5769],[5,5769,6329],[6,6329,10014]]}},{"name":"83:8","price":"スィッジーンが何かを、あなたに何が知らせるか？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا سِجِّينٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5856,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā sijjīnun ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","(is) Sijjin","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","sijjīnun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2320],[2,2320,3380],[3,3380,3720],[4,3720,7575]]}},{"name":"83:9","price":"（その書は、）しっかりと記された¹帳簿である。","arabic":"كِتَٰبٞ مَّرۡقُومٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5857,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　ほかにも、「目印のつけられた」「封印された」という解釈がある（アル＝バガウィー５：２２４参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kitābun marqūmun ","translations":["A book","written","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["kitābun","marqūmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,5135]]}},{"name":"83:10","price":"その日、噓呼ばわりする者たちに災いあれ。","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5858,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Woe","that Day","to the deniers","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1680],[2,1680,2660],[3,2660,6475]]}},{"name":"83:11","price":"報いの日*を、噓呼ばわりする者たちに。","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ يُكَذِّبُونَ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5859,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna yukadhibūna biyawmi al-dīni ","translations":["Those who","deny","(the) Day","(of) the Judgment","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","yukadhibūna","biyawmi","al-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1260],[2,1260,2720],[3,2720,3540],[4,3540,6215]]}},{"name":"83:12","price":"侵犯し、罪に溺れた全ての者以外、それ（報いの日*）を噓呼ばわりしたりはしないというのに。","arabic":"وَمَا يُكَذِّبُ بِهِۦٓ إِلَّا كُلُّ مُعۡتَدٍ أَثِيمٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5860,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yukadhibu bihi illā kullu muʿ'tadin athīmin ","translations":["And not","can deny","[of] it","except","every","transgressor","sinful","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yukadhibu","bihi","illā","kullu","muʿ'tadin","athīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,700],[2,700,1750],[3,1750,3770],[4,3770,4550],[5,4550,5240],[6,5240,6210],[7,6210,9285]]}},{"name":"83:13","price":"われら*の御徴（アーヤ*）がその者に読誦された時、彼は言った。「（これは）昔の人々のお伽話だ」。","arabic":"إِذَا تُتۡلَىٰ عَلَيۡهِ ءَايَٰتُنَا قَالَ أَسَٰطِيرُ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5861,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā tut'lā ʿalayhi āyātunā qāla asāṭīru al-awalīna ","translations":["When","are recited","to him","Our Verses","he says","Stories","(of) the former (people)","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","tut'lā","ʿalayhi","āyātunā","qāla","asāṭīru","al-awalīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,1550],[3,1550,2400],[4,2400,3830],[5,3830,4550],[6,4550,5740],[7,5740,9605]]}},{"name":"83:14","price":"断じて（、彼らの主張は正しく）ない！いや、彼らが稼いでいたもの（罪）が、その心に錆をつけたのである。","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ بَلۡۜ رَانَ عَلَىٰ قُلُوبِهِم مَّا كَانُواْ يَكۡسِبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5862,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā bal rāna ʿalā qulūbihim mā kānū yaksibūna ","translations":["Nay","But","(the) stain has covered","[over]","their hearts","(for) what","they used to","earn","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","bal","rāna","ʿalā","qulūbihim","mā","kānū","yaksibūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,1400],[3,1400,2260],[4,2260,2960],[5,2960,4540],[6,4540,5520],[7,5520,6390],[8,6390,9485]]}},{"name":"83:15","price":"断じて（、彼らの主張は正しく）ない！本当に彼らは（復活の）その日、自分たちの主*（の拝謁）から阻まれている。¹","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهُمۡ عَن رَّبِّهِمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لَّمَحۡجُوبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5863,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　復活の日*に天国の民が、アッラー*を拝見することについては、家畜章１０３とその訳注、ユーヌス*章２６、復活章２３も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innahum ʿan rabbihim yawma-idhin lamaḥjūbūna ","translations":["Nay","Indeed, they","from","their Lord","that Day","surely will be partitioned","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innahum","ʿan","rabbihim","yawma-idhin","lamaḥjūbūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2490],[2,2490,4080],[3,4080,4320],[4,4320,5570],[5,5570,6730],[6,6730,10635]]}},{"name":"83:16","price":"それから本当に彼らは、必ずや火獄に入って炙られる。","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّهُمۡ لَصَالُواْ ٱلۡجَحِيمِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5864,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma innahum laṣālū al-jaḥīmi ","translations":["Then","indeed, they","(surely) will burn","(in) the Hellfire","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","innahum","laṣālū","al-jaḥīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1500],[2,1500,3430],[3,3430,4280],[4,4280,7255]]}},{"name":"83:17","price":"それから、（彼らにはこう）言われるのだ。「これが、あなた方が噓呼ばわりしていたこと（の、報い）である」。","arabic":"ثُمَّ يُقَالُ هَٰذَا ٱلَّذِي كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5865,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma yuqālu hādhā alladhī kuntum bihi tukadhibūna ","translations":["Then","it will be said","This","(is) what","you used to","[of it]","deny","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","yuqālu","hādhā","alladhī","kuntum","bihi","tukadhibūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2120],[3,2120,2710],[4,2710,3610],[5,3610,5090],[6,5090,6340],[7,6340,6920],[8,6920,10425]]}},{"name":"83:18","price":"断じて（、彼らの主張は正しく）ない！本当に善行者¹たちの（行いが記録された）帳簿は、まさにイッリイユーン²の中にある。","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ كِتَٰبَ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارِ لَفِي عِلِّيِّينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5866,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「善行者」については、裂ける章１３の訳注を参照。 ２　この「帳簿」の解釈については、アーヤ*７の訳注を参照。「イッリイユーン」は一説に、「ウルフ（高さ）」という語から派生した言葉で、天国における位の高さ、あるいは高い場所であることが、その名称の由来とされる（イブン・ジュザイ２：５４９参照）。具体的な解釈としては、「天国」「（信仰者の魂が留まる、）天の第七層」「最果てのスィドラ(星章１４の訳注を参照）」「天の第七層の上にある、アッラー*の御座（高壁章５４の訳注を参照）の右足部分」「天使*たちのこと」といった諸説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：２６２－２６３参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā inna kitāba al-abrāri lafī ʿilliyyīna ","translations":["Nay","Indeed","(the) record","(of) the righteous","(will be) surely in","Illiyin","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","inna","kitāba","al-abrāri","lafī","ʿilliyyīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2320],[2,2320,3620],[3,3620,4420],[4,4420,5770],[5,5770,6380],[6,6380,9705]]}},{"name":"83:19","price":"イッリイユーンが何かを、あなたに何が知らせるか？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا عِلِّيُّونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5867,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā ʿilliyyūna ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","(is) Illiyun","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","ʿilliyyūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2050],[2,2050,3080],[3,3080,3520],[4,3520,7145]]}},{"name":"83:20","price":"（その書は、）しっかりと記された¹帳簿である。","arabic":"كِتَٰبٞ مَّرۡقُومٞ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5868,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「しっかりと記された」については、アーヤ*９の９の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kitābun marqūmun ","translations":["A book","written","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["kitābun","marqūmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,4825]]}},{"name":"83:21","price":"側近（天使*）たちが、そこに立ち会う。¹","arabic":"يَشۡهَدُهُ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5869,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　あるいは復活の日*、そこに記されている内容を証言する（アッ＝シャウカーニー５：５３５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yashhaduhu al-muqarabūna ","translations":["Witness it","those brought near","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["yashhaduhu","al-muqarabūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,4615]]}},{"name":"83:22","price":"本当に善行者たちは、必ずや安寧の中に。","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارَ لَفِي نَعِيمٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5870,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna al-abrāra lafī naʿīmin ","translations":["Indeed","the righteous","(will be) surely in","bliss","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","al-abrāra","lafī","naʿīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1530],[2,1530,2830],[3,2830,3410],[4,3410,6265]]}},{"name":"83:23","price":"寝台の上で、（アッラー*と天国の美を）眺めつつ。¹","arabic":"عَلَى ٱلۡأَرَآئِكِ يَنظُرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5871,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"地獄にいる（現世での）自分たちの敵が罰される様子を見る、という解釈もある（アル＝バガウィー５：２２６参照）。包る者章４２の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalā al-arāiki yanẓurūna ","translations":["On","thrones","observing","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalā","al-arāiki","yanẓurūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,3379],[3,3379,7274]]}},{"name":"83:24","price":"あなたは彼らの顔に、安寧の輝きを見出す。","arabic":"تَعۡرِفُ فِي وُجُوهِهِمۡ نَضۡرَةَ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5872,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"taʿrifu fī wujūhihim naḍrata al-naʿīmi ","translations":["You will recognize","in","their faces","(the) radiance","(of) bliss","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["taʿrifu","fī","wujūhihim","naḍrata","al-naʿīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,920],[2,920,1330],[3,1330,2680],[4,2680,3480],[5,3480,7065]]}},{"name":"83:25","price":"彼らは、封印された¹美酒から飲まされる。²","arabic":"يُسۡقَوۡنَ مِن رَّحِيقٖ مَّخۡتُومٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5873,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　天国の民の飲み物については、サード章５１、整列者章４５－４７、詳細にされた章３１、ムハンマド*章１５、出来事章１７－１９、人間章５－６、１７－１８、２１、消息章３４も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yus'qawna min raḥīqin makhtūmin ","translations":["They will be given to drink","of","a pure wine","sealed","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["yus'qawna","min","raḥīqin","makhtūmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1460],[3,1460,2520],[4,2520,6395]]}},{"name":"83:26","price":"その封印¹は、麝香（の風味）。ならば、そこにおいてこそ、競い合う者たちを競い合わせよ。","arabic":"خِتَٰمُهُۥ مِسۡكٞۚ وَفِي ذَٰلِكَ فَلۡيَتَنَافَسِ ٱلۡمُتَنَٰفِسُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5874,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「封印」には、「混ぜ物」「最後の味、あるいは残り香」といった解釈もある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：２６５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"khitāmuhu mis'kun wafī dhālika falyatanāfasi al-mutanāfisūna ","translations":["Its seal","(will be of) musk","And for","that","let aspire","the aspirers","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["khitāmuhu","mis'kun","wafī","dhālika","falyatanāfasi","al-mutanāfisūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,2360],[3,2360,2990],[4,2990,3820],[5,3820,5620],[6,5620,9225]]}},{"name":"83:27","price":"そして、その混ぜ物はタスニーム¹からのもの。","arabic":"وَمِزَاجُهُۥ مِن تَسۡنِيمٍ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5875,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「タスニーム」は「スィナーム（高い場所）」という語から派生した言葉と言われ、高い場所から、天国の民の部屋や家へと流れ注ぐ飲み物。あるいは空中を流れ、彼らの杯にちょうどいい塩梅（あんばい）で注がれる飲み物（アル＝バガウィー５：２２６参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamizājuhu min tasnīmin ","translations":["And its mixture","(is) of","Tasneem","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["wamizājuhu","min","tasnīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1610],[2,1610,2220],[3,2220,5945]]}},{"name":"83:28","price":"（つまり、）側近たち¹がそこから飲む、泉である。","arabic":"عَيۡنٗا يَشۡرَبُ بِهَا ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5876,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「側近たち」は、天国の民でも最良の者たちのこと（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：２６６参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿaynan yashrabu bihā al-muqarabūna ","translations":["A spring","will drink","from it","those brought near","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿaynan","yashrabu","bihā","al-muqarabūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,680],[2,680,2640],[3,2640,3010],[4,3010,6825]]}},{"name":"83:29","price":"本当に、罪悪に手を染めていた者たちは（現世で）、信仰に入った者たちを嘲り笑っていた。","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ أَجۡرَمُواْ كَانُواْ مِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ يَضۡحَكُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5877,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna alladhīna ajramū kānū mina alladhīna āmanū yaḍḥakūna ","translations":["Indeed","those who","committed crimes","used to","at","those who","believed","laugh","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","alladhīna","ajramū","kānū","mina","alladhīna","āmanū","yaḍḥakūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1480],[2,1480,2520],[3,2520,3530],[4,3530,4400],[5,4400,4740],[6,4740,5790],[7,5790,6870],[8,6870,10255]]}},{"name":"83:30","price":"また、彼らのもとを通りかかった時には、（馬鹿にして）目配せし合っていた。","arabic":"وَإِذَا مَرُّواْ بِهِمۡ يَتَغَامَزُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5878,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā marrū bihim yataghāmazūna ","translations":["And when","they passed","by them","they winked at one another","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","marrū","bihim","yataghāmazūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,1800],[3,1800,2380],[4,2380,5765]]}},{"name":"83:31","price":"また、自分たちの家族のもとに帰った時には、（信仰者たちを茶化す話に）興じながら帰ったものだった。","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱنقَلَبُوٓاْ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِمُ ٱنقَلَبُواْ فَكِهِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5879,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā inqalabū ilā ahlihimu inqalabū fakihīna ","translations":["And when","they returned","to","their people","they would return","jesting","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","inqalabū","ilā","ahlihimu","inqalabū","fakihīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,3700],[3,3700,5660],[4,5660,6650],[5,6650,8320],[6,8320,11335]]}},{"name":"83:32","price":"そして彼らを見た時には、（こう）言ったのだ。「本当にこれらの者たちは、まさしく迷った者たちだ」。","arabic":"وَإِذَا رَأَوۡهُمۡ قَالُوٓاْ إِنَّ هَٰٓؤُلَآءِ لَضَآلُّونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5880,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā ra-awhum qālū inna hāulāi laḍāllūna ","translations":["And when","they saw them","they said","Indeed","these","surely have gone astray","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","ra-awhum","qālū","inna","hāulāi","laḍāllūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1850],[3,1850,3850],[4,3850,5100],[5,5100,8900],[6,8900,15075]]}},{"name":"83:33","price":"彼ら（罪悪者たち）は、彼ら（信仰者たち）に監視役¹として遣わされたのではないというのに。","arabic":"وَمَآ أُرۡسِلُواْ عَلَيۡهِمۡ حَٰفِظِينَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5881,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　信仰者たちが迷いの中にあるという虚偽（きょぎ）の主張をすべく、その行いを見守る「監視役」のこと（アッ＝サアディー９１６頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā ur'silū ʿalayhim ḥāfiẓīna ","translations":["But not","they had been sent","over them","(as) guardians","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","ur'silū","ʿalayhim","ḥāfiẓīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2440],[2,2440,3380],[3,3380,4410],[4,4410,7615]]}},{"name":"83:34","price":"ならば、（復活の）その日には、信仰した者たちが不信仰者*たちを笑うのだ。","arabic":"فَٱلۡيَوۡمَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ مِنَ ٱلۡكُفَّارِ يَضۡحَكُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5882,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-yawma alladhīna āmanū mina al-kufāri yaḍḥakūna ","translations":["So today","those who","believed ","at","the disbelievers","they will laugh","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-yawma","alladhīna","āmanū","mina","al-kufāri","yaḍḥakūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1040],[2,1040,2110],[3,2110,3220],[4,3220,3560],[5,3560,4770],[6,4770,8485]]}},{"name":"83:35","price":"寝台の上で、（アッラー*と天国の美を）眺めつつ。¹","arabic":"عَلَى ٱلۡأَرَآئِكِ يَنظُرُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5883,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　アーヤ*２３の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalā al-arāiki yanẓurūna ","translations":["On","the thrones","observing","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalā","al-arāiki","yanẓurūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,490],[2,490,3290],[3,3290,7695]]}},{"name":"83:36","price":"一体、不信仰者*たちは、自分たちが（現世で）していた（罪深い）こと（の応報）を、報われたではないか？¹","arabic":"هَلۡ ثُوِّبَ ٱلۡكُفَّارُ مَا كَانُواْ يَفۡعَلُونَ","category":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin"],"ayahNumber":5884,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　これは、「不信仰者*たちは・・・確かに報われた」という意味を表わす、断定の疑問形（イブン・アーシュール３０：２１５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"hal thuwwiba al-kufāru mā kānū yafʿalūna ","translations":["Have (not)","been rewarded","the disbelievers","(for) what","they used to","do","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["hal","thuwwiba","al-kufāru","mā","kānū","yafʿalūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1330],[3,1330,2830],[4,2830,3260],[5,3260,4270],[6,4270,8765]]}}],"chapter":["83 (Al-Mutaffifin)","Al-Mutaffifin","Surah Al-Mutaffifin","Chapter Al-Mutaffifin","Mutaffifin","Surah Mutaffifin","Chapter Mutaffifin","Al Mutaffifin","Surah Al Mutaffifin","Chapter Al Mutaffifin","Surah 83","Chapter 83","Defrauding","المطففين"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}